company_name: V.L.P. VERTRIEB ITALIENISCHER FOOD PRODUKTE GMBH
information: The company V.L.P. VERTRIEB ITALIENISCHER FOOD PRODUKTE GMBH, is a Wholesaler, founded in 1986, which operates in the Shellfish and crustaceans industry. It also operates in the Fish industries. It is based in Freiberg, Germany.
